# Runtime voice artifacts. The 18 preset voices are binary and fetched at deploy time
# by tts/fetch_voices.py (from the public gepard HuggingFace Space), so they are not
# committed. The one exception is default.pt, the pinned reference voice: regenerating
# it re-rolls the speaker, so the demo voice ships with the repo.
*.pt
!default.pt

# Keep this dir tracked even though its other .pt contents are ignored.
!.gitkeep
